// TaskGraphCard
// Embeds a task execution graph diagram within a card, handling loading, error, and empty states.

FUNCTION TaskGraphCard(props) -> ReactNode                                EXPORT
  CALLS: Card (Card), Spinner (Spinner), Alert (Alert), DiagramEmbed (DiagramEmbed), useTaskGraph (useTaskGraph)
  Fetches task graph data via useTaskGraph for the current project/session.
  IF loading, renders a Spinner inside a Card.
  IF error, renders an Alert with the error message.
  IF no diagram is available, renders an empty-state message.
  IF diagram is available, renders it via DiagramEmbed inside a Card.
